rows.label: tlk43200143_03_msg0001
rows.name: Jillwood? Oh, he's trying so hard!

rows.label: tlk43200143_03_msg0002
rows.name:
With his sword lessons, and his other
lessons... He's got no time to play
anymore, that's how intense it is!

rows.label: tlk43200143_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm afraid he'll get sick
if he doesn't take it easy...

rows.label: tlk43200143_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Maybe I'll ask him to come have
a picnic at Greatmaw Rapids?

rows.label: tlk43200143_03_msg0005
rows.name:
If we get attacked by monsters or
something, it'll be Jillwood's chance
to shine!
